     1â†’/**
     2â†’ * Utility Directives (Tailwind v4 @utility Pattern)
     3â†’ *
     4â†’ * This file contains utility classes using Tailwind v4's @utility directive.
     5â†’ * Converted from @layer utilities for better IDE support, variant generation,
     6â†’ * and @apply compatibility.
     7â†’ *
     8â†’ * Includes:
     9â†’ * - Glass morphism effects (.glass-subtle, .glass-medium, .glass-strong, etc.)
    10â†’ * - Focus ring utilities (.focus-ring, .focus-ring-error, etc.)
    11â†’ * - Accessibility utilities (.skip-link, .focus-visible-only)
    12â†’ */
    13â†’
    14â†’/* ==========================================
    15â†’ * GLASS MORPHISM EFFECTS
    16â†’ * ========================================== */
    17â†’
    18â†’@utility glass-subtle {
